para_trans: To the Hon'ble Minister of State
Reference: - Government Decision, Serial Date: 23 December 2024.
Smt. Madhuri Meera Satish Misal, Hon'ble Minister of State, "Suruchi-18," Churchgate, Mumbai
The decision to allot this government accommodation, which was taken under the relevant government decision, is now being cancelled.
Smt. Madhuri Meera Satish Misaal, Hon'ble Minister of State at "Suruchi-18" at Churchgate
Instead of this government accommodation, the government accommodation "Avanti-6" at Malabar Hill has now been allotted.
The government has taken a decision.
Residence allotted to the Hon'ble Minister of State after he demits office
It will be mandatory to vacate within a period of fifteen days.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
